patthana19.16:1.1_0: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana19.16:1.1_1: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanasappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana19.16:1.1_2: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanaappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana19.16:1.1_3: Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho ca anidassanaappaṭigho
patthana19.16:1.1_4: ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanasappaṭigho
patthana19.16:1.1_5: ca anidassanaappaṭigho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ
patthana19.16:1.1_6: dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho ca anidassanasappaṭigho ca dhammā uppajjanti
patthana19.16:1.1_7: hetupaccayā. Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho ca anidassanasappaṭigho
patthana19.16:1.1_8: ca anidassanaappaṭigho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … satta.
patthana19.16:2.1_0: Naanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanasappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana19.16:2.1_1: Naanidassanasappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … satta.
patthana19.16:3.1: Naanidassanaappaṭighaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca anidassanaappaṭigho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … satta. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana19.16:4.1: Hetuyā pañcatiṁsa, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… aññamaññe dasa …pe… avigate pañcatiṁsa.
